<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>Would it be possible to add a method to set a local path  theme for UI component ? \
Then the specified style sheet will be added if uiIsEnabled()</p>

<pre class="highlight"><code>
$this-&gt;jQuery()-&gt;setUiLocalPathTheme('ui/themes/mytheme/theme.ui.css')
</code></pre>

<p>One of the benefit would be the possibility to defined the theme in the bootstrap and style sheet will be automatically included if needed.</p>

